{"tid":2300580,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 HDMI 2.1 輸出頻寬實測僅得 32Gbps？","createTime":"2020-11-25T15:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T06:07:01.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14b14be7686c9652ede1c2e9e01c7be7d84167b2","tid":2300580,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://post76.hk/news/2020/11/playstation-5-hdmi-2-1-max-32-gbps/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fnews%2F2020%2F11%2Fplaystation-5-hdmi-2-1-max-32-gbps%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=456f7aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://post76.hk/news/2020/11/playstation-5-hdmi-2-1-max-32-gbps/</a><br />\n<br />\n為對應 4K/120Hz 及 8K 影像輸出，Xbox Series X 及 PS5 主機均配備了最新 HDMI 2.1 輸出。然而最近有外媒利用 LG CX 電視機實測發現 PS5 的 HDMI 2.1 輸出的頻寬被硬性限制在 32Gbps 的上限 。根據之前業界的準則 HDMI 2.1 的可應對的頻寬應達 48Gbps，而當前所發現的 32Gbps 數據量剛好是峰值的 2/3 左右。相比下 Xbox Series X 則有輕微優勢，流量峰值能達 40Gbps。換言之兩款主機在開啟 4K/120Hz 模式後，PS5 只能顯示 YUV 4:2:2 的顔色採樣，而 Xbox Series X 則能做出 4：4：4 的規格，在畫面上表現更佳。然而 PS5 能支援「固定傳輸連結」 FRL（Fixed Rate Link），在 4K/120Hz（或 8K/60Hz）模式上能做出更好的編碼效率表現。令人疑惑時目前尚未有資料能清晰指出 PS5 的 HDMI 2.1 頻寬限制是否能透過軟件升級解決。"},{"pid":"229dbb54f4b6791529b2c0d885c78f6f57f3b399","tid":2300580,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D7pKgscRpN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD7pKgscRpN8&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=5ccc4910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D7pKgscRpN8</a>"},{"pid":"a027c5c69faca968d2201c4241a30d6217b133f4","tid":2300580,"uid":225422,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"買你就買啦<br />\n日撚日引戰"},{"pid":"4bb8eaaa6b7623c743abb33306b1d5e8d55b49e3","tid":2300580,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T0